{"tid":1503104,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Diablo2] 美國毒撚朋友都好關心我地香港!!","createTime":"2019-08-24T22:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T17:52:57.000Z","uid":45616,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b151b37f00651be26a7fb364723f65c263358d","tid":1503104,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T22:28:29.000Z","msg":"唔知開係咩台好<br />\n<br />\n話說小弟只係一個小小既毒撚<br />\n毒到仲玩緊Diablo 2呢隻幾十年前既game<br />\n由於我地個交易網會Show到你係邊到人<br />\n賣賣下野都比人發現我係香港人，原來連美國一個毒撚都有留意我地呢邊發生緊咩事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PGD8uGH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPGD8uGH.png&h=3ef13f34&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由下至上睇<br />\n<br />\n之後入Game交易都同佢傾左兩句<br />\n雖然只係一個素未謀面既美國人<br />\n但都好關心我地香港發生既事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4C7JiAB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4C7JiAB.png&h=41ebe982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由下至上睇<br />\n<br />\n最後佢同我講左句stay safe<br />\n我地平時玩Hardcore mode，trade完會講句stay safe<br />\n因為Hardcore mode死左隻角色就會真係死，乜都冇晒果隻<br />\n但今次我玩緊既係softcore，隻角色死左都冇所謂<br />\n但香港人就唔同，大家都要stay safe"},{"pid":"993d5b6748ed60c75b506505bdca2e5b120a731a","tid":1503104,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T22:28:51.000Z","msg":"［開飯/住宿/義診/搵工］你班前線死廢青 未成年中學雞同我入黎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503091</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b61f89dfde4601b2c4fde175fa97046113236932","tid":1503104,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T22:31:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b1a750088cc3974d55d433fe29bac566e72ebe4e","tid":1503104,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T22:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8